column1: Strains Present In this Data Sheet:

Data Present: 220920 Nor MIC at 80, 40, 20, 10 and 0 ng/mL. Because JOE7051 and JOE7052 have the same genotype, their OD600 readings are averaged per concentration and time interval.
Averages per Concentration and Strain are calculated here. JOE7051 and JOE7052 are grouped together as previously done, with only JOE7052 included from the 7/28 assay.
Example: for JOE6970 at 80 ng/mL Nor at about 30 minutes, the averaged value from of all five experiments for that cell at that time is calculated.
Standard Deviations are measured per time Interval at a given concentration across all strains present.
Example: for JOE6970 at 80 ng/mL Nor at about 30 minutes, the SD from of all five experiments for that cell at that time is calculated.
